  \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"基于系统拓扑（Cart→Redis），cartservice的严重延迟和连接超时表明底层Redis存储可能存在问题，导致cartservice无法正常访问数据\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现分析：\n\n**根因定位**：\n- **cartservice** 是明确的故障根因，所有frontend实例对cartservice的调用都出现严重延迟和连接错误\n- 错误状态码分析显示大量超时和连接被拒绝错误，表明cartservice服务不可用或响应极慢\n\n**延迟分析**：\n- CartService/GetCart：延迟倍数13-22倍（正常3-25秒 → 异常51-56秒）\n- CartService/AddItem：延迟倍数约10倍（正常5秒 → 异常49-55秒）\n\n**错误传播路径**：\n1. Redis存储层可能存在问题（基于拓扑Cart→Redis）\n2. cartservice无法正常访问Redis，导致服务不可用\n3. frontend调用cartservice时出现超时和连接错误\n4. 最终用户看到HTTP 500错误\n\n**建议**：需要检查cartservice的健康状态和Redis连接情况，这是明确的根因服务。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet\n\n--- Metric Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nAGREED", "log_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "report_analysis_findings": {"uuid": "a363d826-117", "component": "cartservice", "reason": "cartservice connection errors causing i/o timeout and transport is closing errors, error_ratio spike to 49.19%", "reasoning_trace": [{"step": 1, "action": "LogSearch(cartservice)", "observation": "Found context canceled, transport is closing, i/o timeout errors targeting 10.233.46.196:7070"}, {"step": 2, "action": "LoadMetrics(cartservice)", "observation": "error_ratio increased from 0% to 49.19% across all cartservice pods"}, {"step": 3, "action": "TraceAnalysis(a363d826-117)", "observation": "CartService/GetCart latency increased 13-22x from 3-25s to 51-56s"}]}, "report_analysis_completed": true}
